{% comment %}
  Home page. Renders a brand grid from `aico_shop_brands` (every brand on the
  shop, annotated with `aico_is_accessible?` per the current shopper, in the
  per-shop order set in the admin). Accessible tiles link to `/brand/{handle}`
  (matching the drawer brand picker's URL pattern); inaccessible tiles render
  greyed-out and non-clickable so the user knows which brands exist but
  aren't on their plan.

  WHICH brands appear here is curated BY THIS THEME, not by the backend: this
  home page is a hand-made landing page, so `aico_home_brand_keys` below is the
  guest list. A brand the shop carries but this list omits still works
  everywhere else (brand picker, /brand/<handle>, search) — it simply isn't one
  of the tiles on this page. Order still comes from the admin (the per-shop
  brand order), so reordering in Neo reorders these tiles too.

  Edit `aico_home_brand_keys` to change the tiles. Each entry matches either a
  brand's url handle or its numeric id — ids are per-environment (each env has
  its own copy of this theme), so prefer handles where the brands have them.
  An EMPTY list means "show every brand the shop carries", which is what a
  generic shop wants. So does a list that matches NOTHING: the grid fails open
  rather than rendering a blank page when the keys are wrong for this env.

  Tile layout: top region uses `brand.aico_image_tile_url` (the dedicated
  tile photo) falling back to `brand.image_url` (banner or lifestyle).
  The footer strip resolves its logo the same way the header does —
  `brand.logo_url | default: brand.image_url` — so a brand that has logo
  artwork always shows it on both surfaces; only a brand with no artwork
  at all falls back to the text label.

  Disabled tiles are sorted to the bottom by `ShopAllBrandsLoader`
  (mirrors b2b-shop's `transformHomePage` `orderBy(isAccessible, desc)`).

  Site-wide footer renders from `layout/theme.liquid` (linklists.footer).

  TODO: hero band / "Beliebte Modelle" / news strip — punted to a later
  slice. The pre-existing `home_page.popular_models` / `home_page.news`
  locale keys stay shipped so other slices can reuse them.
{% endcomment %}

{%- comment -%} The curated tile list — see the note at the top of this file. {%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign aico_home_brand_keys = 'kybun,joya,kybunjoya,kandahar,kybun-arabic-styles,special-edition,3,6,7,8,10,13' | split: ',' -%}

{%- comment -%}
  Count the matches first: if the keys match nothing here (wrong env, renamed
  handles), the page shows every brand instead of nothing.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign aico_home_curated_count = 0 -%}
{%- for brand in aico_shop_brands -%}
  {%- assign aico_brand_id_key = brand.id | append: '' -%}
  {%- if aico_home_brand_keys contains aico_brand_id_key -%}
    {%- assign aico_home_curated_count = aico_home_curated_count | plus: 1 -%}
  {%- elsif brand.url_handle and aico_home_brand_keys contains brand.url_handle -%}
    {%- assign aico_home_curated_count = aico_home_curated_count | plus: 1 -%}
  {%- endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}

<main class="aico-home aico-home-brands-page" role="main">
  <section class="aico-page-container aico-home-brand-section">
    <h1 class="aico-home-brand-heading">{{ 'home_page.choose_brand' | t }}</h1>

    {% if aico_shop_brands.size > 0 %}
      <ul class="aico-home-brand-grid" role="list">
        {% for brand in aico_shop_brands %}
          {%- assign aico_brand_id_key = brand.id | append: '' -%}
          {%- assign aico_brand_is_curated = false -%}
          {%- if aico_home_curated_count == 0 -%}
            {%- assign aico_brand_is_curated = true -%}
          {%- elsif aico_home_brand_keys contains aico_brand_id_key -%}
            {%- assign aico_brand_is_curated = true -%}
          {%- elsif brand.url_handle and aico_home_brand_keys contains brand.url_handle -%}
            {%- assign aico_brand_is_curated = true -%}
          {%- endif -%}
          {%- if aico_brand_is_curated -%}
          <li class="aico-home-brand-grid-item">
            {% if brand.aico_is_accessible? %}
              <form
                method="post"
                action="{{ routes.aico_account_select_brand_url }}"
                class="aico-home-brand-card-form"
              >
                <input type="hidden" name="_token" value="{{ aico_csrf_token }}">
                <input type="hidden" name="brand_id" value="{{ brand.id }}">
                <input type="hidden" name="return_url" value="{{ brand.url }}">
                <button
                  type="submit"
                  class="aico-home-brand-card aico-home-brand-card-accessible"
                  aria-label="{{ brand.label }}"
                >
                  {%- assign aico_card_photo = brand.aico_image_tile_url | default: brand.image_url -%}
                  <div class="aico-home-brand-card-photo-wrap">
                    {% if aico_card_photo %}
                      <img
                        src="{{ aico_card_photo }}"
                        alt=""
                        class="aico-home-brand-card-photo"
                        loading="lazy"
                        decoding="async"
                      >
                    {% else %}
                      <div class="aico-home-brand-card-photo-empty" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                    {% endif %}
                  </div>
                  {%- assign aico_card_logo = brand.logo_url | default: brand.image_url -%}
                  <div class="aico-home-brand-card-footer">
                    {% if aico_card_logo %}
                      <img
                        src="{{ aico_card_logo }}"
                        alt="{{ brand.label }}"
                        class="aico-home-brand-card-logo"
                        loading="lazy"
                        decoding="async"
                      >
                    {% else %}
                      <span class="aico-home-brand-card-label">{{ brand.label }}</span>
                    {% endif %}
                  </div>
                </button>
              </form>
            {% else %}
              <div
                class="aico-home-brand-card aico-home-brand-card-disabled"
                aria-disabled="true"
                title="{{ 'home_page.brand_inaccessible' | t }}"
              >
                {%- assign aico_card_photo = brand.aico_image_tile_url | default: brand.image_url -%}
                <div class="aico-home-brand-card-photo-wrap">
                  {% if aico_card_photo %}
                    <img
                      src="{{ aico_card_photo }}"
                      alt=""
                      class="aico-home-brand-card-photo"
                      loading="lazy"
                      decoding="async"
                    >
                  {% else %}
                    <div class="aico-home-brand-card-photo-empty" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                  {% endif %}
                </div>
                {%- assign aico_card_logo = brand.logo_url | default: brand.image_url -%}
                <div class="aico-home-brand-card-footer">
                  {% if aico_card_logo %}
                    <img
                      src="{{ aico_card_logo }}"
                      alt="{{ brand.label }}"
                      class="aico-home-brand-card-logo"
                      loading="lazy"
                      decoding="async"
                    >
                  {% else %}
                    <span class="aico-home-brand-card-label">{{ brand.label }}</span>
                  {% endif %}
                  <span class="aico-sr-only">{{ 'home_page.brand_inaccessible' | t }}</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            {% endif %}
          </li>
          {%- endif -%}
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    {% else %}
      <p class="aico-home-brand-empty">{{ 'home_page.no_brands' | t }}</p>
    {% endif %}
  </section>

</main>
